text: Liao Qiuyun (, born 13 July 1995) is a Chinese female weightlifter, World Champion, and Asian Champion competing in the 55 kg division.2019 World Championships Entry List ==Career== In early 2019 she competed at the 2019 IWF World Cup in the 55 kg division and won gold medals in all lifts.2019 IWF World Cup Results Book Later in 2019 she competed at the 2019 Asian Weightlifting Championships in the 55 kg category, won gold medals in all lifts, and set a world record in the clean & jerk with a lift of 128 kg.
